### AUTH
POST http://localhost:3000/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@example.com",
  "password": "AdminPass123!"
}

### REFRESH
POST http://localhost:3000/api/auth/refresh
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "refreshToken": "{{refreshToken}}"
}

### LOGOUT (replace {{accessToken}})
POST http://localhost:3000/api/auth/logout
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "refreshToken": "{{refreshToken}}"
}

### ADMIN create teacher
POST http://localhost:3000/api/admin/users
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "New Teacher",
  "email": "new-teacher@example.com",
  "password": "Teacher#1",
  "role": "TEACHER"
}

### ADMIN list users
GET http://localhost:3000/api/admin/users?page=1&limit=10&role=TEACHER
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### ADMIN assign student
POST http://localhost:3000/api/admin/assign-student
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "teacherId": "{{teacherId}}",
  "studentId": "{{studentId}}"
}

### TEACHER list students
GET http://localhost:3000/api/teacher/students?page=1&limit=10
Authorization: Bearer {{teacherAccessToken}}

### TEACHER create group
POST http://localhost:3000/api/teacher/groups
Authorization: Bearer {{teacherAccessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Group A"
}

### TEACHER add student to group
POST http://localhost:3000/api/teacher/groups/{{groupId}}/add-student
Authorization: Bearer {{teacherAccessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "studentId": "{{studentId}}"
}

### CHAT private history (teacher<->student)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/chat/private/{{otherUserId}}?page=1&limit=20
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### CHAT group history
GET http://localhost:3000/api/chat/group/{{groupId}}?page=1&limit=20
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
